@startuml
title **SRM用户使用分析**
:Main Admin: as Admin
(账户管理) as (am)
(角色管理) as (rm)
(功能管理) as (fm)
(系统监控) as (sm)

Admin --> (am)
Admin --> (rm)
Admin --> (fm)
Admin --> (sm)

:Sys User: as User
(协议创建) as (brc)
(协议确认) as (src)
(金额确认) as (sac)
(金额推送) as (bap)

User --> (brc)
User --> (src)
User --> (sac)
User --> (bap)

@enduml
